v1.0.4

2019-07-10 
- Added timestamp conversion of various languages to ISO 8601 (issue #7) 
  format and added @when-iso in the posting element.  
- Added change log.
2019-07-10
- Renamed <autoSignature> to <signed> and <timestamp> to <date>  
2019-07-16
- Fixed person name recognition and add <name> in <signed> element.
2019-07-24
- Added more criteria for identifying empty pages (issue #10).
- Fixed missing start text in user-talk signature handler.
- Added <ref> to <signed> for user-link signatures (issue #11).
2019-07-25
- Added <ref> to signatures with user-discussion-links (issue #11) and 
  updated adding signatures after parsing wikitext.

